Package: ProCESS
Type: Package
Title: ProCESS: Programmable Cancer Evolution Spatial Simulator
Version: 1.0.5
Date: 2025-06-13
Authors@R: c(
    person("Alberto", "Casagrande", email = "alberto.casagrande@uniud.it", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Giulio", "Caravagna", role = c("aut")))
Maintainer: Alberto Casagrande <alberto.casagrande@uniud.it>
Description: ProCESS is an R wrapper for RACES and provides
        additional plotting functions. It supports spacial
        evolution of different mutants, different epigenetic
        mutant states, timed-triggered driver mutations.
URL: https://caravagnalab.github.io/ProCESS
